name: The Mad Hatter's Club VIP Mint Pass
description:
PRIORITY MINT PASS REDEEMABLE FOR ONE MAD HATTER’S CLUB NFT DROP

The pass entitles you to obtain a bunny at drop price, before it enters the market. 

The Mad Hatter’s Club must be informed of redemption
before the drop takes place and is made open to the public through the Mad Hatter's Club Discord Server.
 
This pass cannot be used for 1-1 collectors editions. 
Only 1 pass can be used person per drop. This pass does not infer the right to a free or discounted bunny. Only to have priority access to a mint.  
The Mad Hatter’s Club reserves the right of refusal if the pass is not used in good faith.

This pass CAN be traded or sold.
